{"hf85ff6bfg0c66g4744gbd7eg7cefa1a8c0c1": ["Wake up.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "d1e6122b-fea4-983a-f788-c5b1e96b83d1"], "h189d387cg3b8ag4a6aga32bg5562535dcac5": ["*Your face aches, like your jaw's been wrenched asunder. Your tongue is lead, skull eager to burst.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "7998ec2e-245a-f60b-6720-360809dd8e0e"], "h8b44536cg42c5g45ecgaa99g17c5cb7437c9": ["Why won't you let me in? Can't you feel what's happening?", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "15dea6fb-a8ab-4428-c505-a2ead50559a6"], "hed0a0190g538ag41aeg9208g3e6fae30590b": ["Tell me how. I'll do anything to make this stop.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "646f09eb-53f3-ae80-12e2-90a0f3d0a66b"], "hba5dd640g3be5g4542g883aga1f80266d4c1": ["Agony suits you. Suffering, less so.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "c7a515dd-20cf-fba3-509d-ea0a80a89327"], "h91b6ed82g5cf1g4d64gae77g1ec2010976c2": ["Take a deep breath and relax. I need to go deeper.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "a9b98902-9439-8fff-94a7-f4a95478c10f"], "h16d3061cg90c1g4a4bg8726ge068d4884aa6": ["*Nausea twists your stomach, but it's hunger, not revulsion.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "7a1f1639-29e0-ad85-dbfc-8f733dcf19b7"], "h6ed5c9dfg22a8g4a5fga338g1bfd313b7163": ["*Something inside you clamours for blood, for death, and only the tear of flesh will do.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "ab0f4cb1-57c2-21b8-857e-946f7a59ca34"], "he882be23g0856g437cga665gd4661e3648ef": ["*It wants <i>her.*</i>", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "c18b14de-7ad2-f540-69bd-160c0958a6b7"], "he1c993ecgf473g415cg9bdbg39bef3a1fcf3": ["*It wants <i>him.*</i>", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "c18b14de-7ad2-f540-69bd-160c0958a6b7"], "h974525bfg00c9g40e2g933cg3aeb2fc060e7": ["<i>Resist both her and the urge.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "1e2b40f7-d54e-5f0e-4d41-c2513eac5282"], "h0bb6c688gac60g4e1ega107gd30e063b0691": ["<i>Resist both him and the urge.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "1e2b40f7-d54e-5f0e-4d41-c2513eac5282"], "hf63f191dgc5a5g4a4fg9469g71d874990d59": ["You disgust me. So utterly ungrateful.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "d991fabc-2631-937f-8742-c0052c271766"], "h7e5fed24gd37bg43cbg830agba21a6635320": ["I'll find you again. And next time, you'll beg me for forgiveness.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "fe24b486-2b67-7f99-3db7-c605892bde3e"], "hc9b103d7gf815g43f6g8699g063714a8bc48": ["Shh, now. Don't struggle.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "4938ba64-5362-db05-2801-b147bb61b7df"], "h02ba63d8g58a7g4947ga7a3gf213eb94deb1": ["This is what was meant to be. And soon, we'll have everything.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "cf2092b3-8536-608d-672c-109328631d02"], "h4a7a5938g6bc6g4c3agbf32g50617ef198f7": ["I can't wait to see you again.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "15b4ed43-ae41-6fee-a3f1-27068446e750"], "hf6f3aa90ga06bg4b0bgbffag14b0bd4e821d": ["<i>Surrender to the urge - lash out.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "6e46dfac-cc0b-efa6-985a-61b22a08a675"], "h5295f03cge334g4af2gb70ag3c23d65170e9": ["You... monster.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "bc835fdc-b928-6ced-a522-c2d87076031e"], "hadb2f832g70f7g4e21g8802g7f6c78904234": ["You deserve everything that's coming for you. ", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "9da77a66-19f9-0e7d-8a5a-10744a2d751f"], "h6b17fb25gc4e0g4c96g93bcg8079f034ede6": ["Good <i>night.</i>", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "b1bc3c13-090a-9101-ed2c-50694527e90c"], "hb03a70d7gbb50g4086gb05dgacb033767d4f": ["I want to rip you open. I can't help it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "65987207-fb84-c693-9080-8ddd5447101e"], "hfced4fb6gca68g4a93ga238gd3f49e54731c": ["I know. But you'll keep fighting, won't you?", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "8aa37631-7c51-ab36-c79f-37692978b0d9"], "h80ddcd22gd838g4bccg99b6g33959a68fb2d": ["We'll find each other, and everything will be all right.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "3371ebe4-d3ea-124e-aec0-1f950b8dcfd3"], "h57df7325gcd5eg4fccg810bga24ee7a15db6": ["I'm not fighting you! It's this wretched parasite.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "56fe8e2d-2053-0dd5-8d1c-949ec61f416c"], "he2041410g1105g41d2gb688gdeda97e8194a": ["Ah... you're not conscious of it, are you?", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "7c73ae83-0114-6bf4-06d2-6f13863fae37"], "h9a9a261ag1606g4726gb60dg6aeaf8dbd45e": ["Some animal part of you is thrashing about.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "4c52916b-6ee8-1cad-5ca5-db4212585b19"], "he5480166g63b1g499dg943ag78bd98af0f00": ["Let me quiet the beast down.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "05702905-02e2-a97a-b75a-f81f665b1f80"], "hea4a573ege0ceg48bcg8459g30e2ebb9f3bc": ["Of course I can feel it. This is <i>you!</i> It has been from the start.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "c9da1eab-ee1b-6a25-ca1b-5e0e7fcfd503"], "hf30af46eg1ad2g4749gbe0eg016093e57254": ["How dare you? After everything I've sacrificed to get us this far.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "cd1b3dec-934d-b5ed-c1a1-484d5098325c"], "he1f903d9gf974g462dg8100g74522bf4310a": ["I don't want to rip you apart, darling.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "c0e50cb0-22c6-d843-345e-7156a098198a"], "hac095cb2gd566g4ff1g84abg45a27ab7170e": ["I want us to be <i>together.</i>", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy3_AvD_ROM.html", "15f5c613-19ab-2c48-d285-8ef2324871e0"]}